<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The value attribute of a Zend_Form_Element_Submit appears to be tightly coupled with the id and name attributes. Thus, it is not possible to set a value independent of the element's name/id. This also prevents one from displaying spaces in the submit button value (e.g. "Add Category").</p>

    </div>
